NAME
    KiokuDB::Backend::CouchDB - CouchDB backend for KiokuDB

SYNOPSIS
        KiokuDB->connect( "couchdb:uri=http://127.0.0.1:5984/database" );

DESCRIPTION
    This backend provides KiokuDB support for CouchDB using
    AnyEvent::CouchDB.

DEBUGGING
    Set the environment variable KIOKU_COUCH_TRACE if you want debug output
    describing what CouchDB bound requests are being processed.

TRANSACTION SUPPORT
    This backend does not currently support transactions.

ATTRIBUTES
    db  An AnyEvent::CouchDB::Database instance.

        Required.

    create
        Whether or not to try and create the database on instantiaton.

        Defaults to false.

SEE ALSO
    KiokuX::CouchDB::Role::View.

VERSION CONTROL
    <http://github.com/mzedeler/kiokudb-backend-couchdb>

